<h2>JavaScript Operators</h2>

<p>x = 5<br> y = 2<br> calculate z = x + y<br> and display z<br></p>

<p id="demo"></p>

<script>
var x = 5;
var y = 2;
var z = x + y;
document.getElementById("demo").innerHTML = z;
</script>

</body>
